data.description: Amazing opportunity to own land in Hunt County with no restrictions!  3 acre, fenced lot outside the city limits. Current mobile home on the property is 4 beds and 3 full baths; in need of full remodel and repair. Seller makes no warranties on condition. Selling AS-IS. Mobile home could also be removed to bring in your own. See the virtual tour.
